                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-14 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Streamline your workflow with our powerful ticket management system. Track, organize, and resolve issues faster than ever before.
                </p>
                <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
                    {# {% if not isAuthenticated() %} #}
                        <a href="?route=auth/signup" class="btn btn-1  font-semibold shadow-lg">Get Started</a>
